msgid "High-performance Rust DNS forwarder with caching and adaptive multi-path failover."
msgstr "高性能 Rust DNS 转发器，内置缓存与自适应多路故障转移。"

msgid "High-performance DNS forwarder written in Rust: configurable cache, serve-stale, prefetch, and adaptive failover that races multiple upstreams (UDP/TCP/DoT/DoH) and takes the fastest answer."
msgstr "使用 Rust 编写的高性能 DNS 转发器：可配置缓存、过期应答（serve-stale）、预取，以及自适应故障转移——并发竞速多个上游（UDP/TCP/DoT/DoH），采用最快的应答。"

